Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.31,0:02:03.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(神楽)ﾌﾞﾌ… ﾌﾞﾌﾌﾌ…\N変な顔～！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.77,0:02:13.64,On Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an9}[Shinpachi]
